title: The Anarchist's Wife
description:
The Anarchist's Wife

A moving drama about the undying love and suffering of a couple affected by the Spanish Civil War over several decades. Manuela is left behind when her husband Justo fights for his ideals against Franco's Nationalists during the Spanish Civil War. When he disappears for many years, Manuela never gives up hope of seeing him again. Directed by Marie Noelle and Peter Sehr, and stars MarÃƒÂ­a Valverde, Juan Diego Botto and Ivana Baquero.
